                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 351.117/31.</note>
                <head ana="#head_untitled-inferred-from-preceding-sibling-head">[Untitled]</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">American Embassy</hi>, <lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Paris</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1915-01-14">
                            <hi rend="italic">January 14, 1915</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>453. Department’s 452, January 5. Representations made as directed. In reply,
                    French Minister for Foreign Affairs declines to intervene in behalf of
                    Chandeysson, using same arguments as in case Peralme, reported in my 452.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Sharp</hi>.</signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
